 <chunk id="ch443" type="p">
  <sentence id="s443">
   <ns/>
   <tok>
    <orth>,</orth>
    <lex disamb="1"><base>,</base><ctag>interp</ctag></lex>
   </tok>
   <tok>
    <orth>organów</orth>
    <lex disamb="1"><base>organ</base><ctag>subst:pl:gen:m3</ctag></lex>
